31 日，其姐姐在下班后接孩子回家的路上，遇到一辆大货车侧翻，车上装载的沥青顺势流下。其姐姐和侄子被高温沥青烫伤，送医后不治身亡。 「已经到村口拐弯处了，离家只有两三公里，事后发现货车超载 25 倍，当时躲避其他车辆没办法控制方向。」邹女士说，截至目前，他们没有收到任何道歉，货车司机已被警方控制，车辆挂靠公司和沥青混凝土公司一直没有露面。 ↑事发现场 红星新闻记者从警方办案人员处了解到，目前，嫌疑人已被依法逮捕，案件还在侦查阶段。记者联系涉事运输公司及沥青混凝土公司，未获回应。福州一母子被洒落沥青烫伤身亡，涉事车辆超载 25 倍，运输公司多次上「黑榜」_ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/607112600"}}, "attached_info": "ClMIteb3zpikrIE3EAMaCDk3MTk0MzkzINOdtKQGMAA4E0Aocgg5NzE5NDM5M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1686974676.799247", "card_id": "Q_605219932", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "汽车长期静置不用，有什么安全隐患需要注意吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-245bd20b963aeddb0cbc11da41efcf70_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/605219932"}}, "attached_info": "ClMIteb3zpikrIE3EAMaCDk2NzczMzg2IOKY/6MGMAA4KUApcgg5Njc3MzM4NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1686974676.799724", "card_id": "Q_587575758", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "电视剧《知否知否应是绿肥红瘦》中有哪些值得打卡的名场面？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8cf2a1439a014ee656836ba71a49eed4_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu